Amended Information filed amending Count 1 to exposing genitals contrary to sec. 948.10(1)(b) of the Wisconsin Statutes.
State moves to dismiss and read in Count 2.  Motion granted.
Count 1 - Guilty plea to amended charge.  Convicted.
Sentence is withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years.  Conditions of probation:
1) COMPAS assessment and follow through;
2) Continue current counseling program or agent recommended alternative;
3) No contact with the victim;
4) Contact with minors at agents discretion except defendants biological children;
5) Maintain full-time employment;
6) Provide a DNA sample and pay surcharge;
7) Sixty (60) days Manitowoc County Jail, Huber Law, commencing 06-07-16 by 8:00 a.m.; 
8) Pay costs of the action (apply bail); and
9) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Minutes.
